create a hcl file like below values:
=====================================
azure.pkr.hcl ==> create outside of the git repo
client_id="xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx"
subscription_id="xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx"
tenant_id="xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx"
client_secret="xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx"


Prerequisites:
=============
1.go
2.ansible
3.azure cli
4.packer
5.terraform 

commands: 
==========

ssh-keygen 

copy pub and private key into root folder
sudo chmod 400 id_rsa
sudo chmod 644 id_rsa.pub

go mod init github.com/satyamuralidhar/terratest/lampserver
go mod tidy
go test -v -timeout 60m



